A '''caf dispenser''' was a small machine that produced and dispensed ready-to-drink [[Caf/Legends|caf]]. A caf dispenser was a common sight in [[Starship/Legends|starships]] because they could keep the [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] or crew awake on long voyages.

